6 An Act relating to sheriffs; amending 19 O.S. 2021,
Section 547, as amended by Section 1, Chapter 325,
7 O.S.L. 2024 (19 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 547), which
relates to deputizing certain persons; authorizing
8 submission of certain resolution to board of county
commissioners; stating resolution criteria;
9 authorizing certain duties for certain peace
officers; stating certain liability and
10 responsibilities; requiring certain resolution; and
providing an effective date.
